出行一客。
Take a trip.
《财经》杂志交通工业组创建，专注于交通出行领域新闻。
The Transport Industry Section of Caijing Magazine was founded to focus on news in the field of transport travel.
在这里，我们将带你联结出行、科技与未来。
Here, we will connect you with travel, technology and the future.
。
.
首都机场对所有入境人员采取集中隔离措施，表明北京防控压力陡增，为此迅速采取各种有效防控手段，符合各方面的共同诉求沈阳驻京办事处工作人员在准备对接旅客文|《财经》记者陈亮 姚佳莹编辑|施智梁 朱弢为了舒缓北京首都机场防控外来疫情输入的压力，此前盛传的首都机场国际航班分流周边城市的方案已出台，将从3月20日正式付诸实施。
The intensive quarantine measures taken by the Capital Airport for all incoming passengers show that Beijing is under increasing pressure to prevent and control the disease. As a result, Beijing has taken prompt and effective measures to prevent and control the disease.
3月19日晚间，民航局、外交部、国家卫生健康委、海关总署、移民局联合发布《关于目的地为北京的国际客运航班有关事宜的公告》（下简称公告），决定调整目的地为北京的部分国际航班从指定第一入境点入境。
On the evening of March 19, the Civil Aviation Administration, the Ministry of Foreign Affairs, the National Health Commission, the General Administration of Customs and the Immigration Bureau jointly issued the Notice on Matters Relating to International Passenger Flight to Beijing (hereinafter referred to as the Notice) and decided to adjust the entry of some international flights destined for Beijing from designated first entry points.
公告称，将调整部分国际始发客运航班从指定第一入境点入境：北京时间3月20日莫斯科至北京CA910航班、3月22日巴黎至北京CA934航班第一入境点为天津；3月20—22日东京至北京CA926航班第一入境点为呼和浩特；3月21—22日多伦多至北京HU7976航班第一入境点为太原。
The notice said that some international passenger departures would be re-routed from designated first entry points: Beijing, March 20; Beijing, CA910; Paris, 22 March, Paris, to Beijing, CA934, Tianjin; Tokyo, 22 March, flight CA926, Hohhot, Tokyo, 22 March; and Taiyuan, the first point of entry for flight HU7976 from Toronto to Beijing, March 21-22.
乘坐上述国际航班的旅客在第一入境点实施检疫并办理入境手续，行李清关。
Passengers travelling on the above-mentioned international flights undergo quarantine and entry formalities and baggage clearance at the first point of entry.
检疫符合登机条件的旅客可搭乘原航班入京。
Quarantine eligible passengers can take the original flight to Beijing.
腹舱所带货物在北京清关。
The cargo in the belly is cleared in Beijing.
根据公告，目的地为北京的国际航班指定第一入境点的安排及相关措施，将根据疫情变化情况适时调整。
According to the announcement, the arrangement of designating the first entry point for international flights destined for Beijing and related measures will be adjusted according to the changing situation of the epidemic.
民航局将根据疫情防控的整体要求，加强与各部门的协同配合，严密制定工作方案，指导民航各运行单位加强风险管控，进一步严格做好机上防控消毒，确保航班运行安全有序。
In accordance with the overall requirements of epidemic prevention and control, the Civil Aviation Administration will strengthen coordination and coordination with various departments, closely formulate work plans, guide civil aviation operational units to strengthen risk control, further strictly control and disinfection on board, and ensure the safe and orderly operation of the flight.
民航局将加强与地方政府的对接，和相关部门共同推进入境疫情防控“数据共享、人员处置、防控合作”机制落地，织密织牢联防联控网络。
The Civil Aviation Administration will strengthen the interface with local governments, and work with relevant departments to promote the entry of disease prevention and control "data sharing, personnel handling, prevention and control cooperation" mechanism landing, knitted tightly linked control network.
值得注意的是，上述公告是第1号公告。
It is worth noting that the above-mentioned proclamation is Proclamation No. 1.
后续接收地机场保障跟上，航司人员配置跟上后，或出现更多分流公告。
Airport security at subsequent receiving locations keeps pace, and the staffing of the Division keeps pace, or there may be more diversion announcements.
新国展外围的公园已封锁罗兰贝格管理咨询公司全球合伙人于占福告诉《财经》记者，此次多部门联合发布的新政策，在整个中国民航界都属首次。
The park on the periphery of the new China National Exhibition has blocked off the new multi-agency policy, the first of its kind in China's civil aviation industry, Yu told Caijing, a global partner at Rolanberger Management Consulting.
其联合部门之多，涉及到的具体操作流程和管理制度的复杂性之巨，在中国民航历史上都堪称突破。
Its joint departments, involving the specific operating procedures and management system complexity, in the history of CAAC can be regarded as a breakthrough.
对于目前已经造成全球20多万确诊病例，所有有人类常驻大洲无一幸免的“全球大流行”疫情的冲击，于占福认为，已经没有同等量级的先例经验可循，且疫情的全球局势变化速度相当快，每天都有非常复杂的新情况出现，面对这样一个无先前经验可供参考的挑战，多部门联合协作，打破常规、灵活创新、勇于突破是非常必要的举措。
With more than 200,000 confirmed cases worldwide, all of which have been hit by a global pandemic without sparing no other continent, Zhang believes that there is no comparable precedent to follow, and that the global situation of the epidemic is changing at a fairly rapid pace, with very complex new situations emerging every day.
首都机场分流也预期之内，北京面临输入性病例增多的难题，必须采取有效应对措施。
Capital airport diversion is also expected, Beijing faces the problem of an increase in imported cases, must take effective measures.
3月19日北京共新增境外输入确诊病例6例，疑似病例6例。
On March 19, a total of 6 confirmed cases and 6 suspected cases were added to Beijing.
截至3月19日24时，累计报告境外输入确诊病例70例，治愈出院病例6例。
As of 2400 hours on March 19, a cumulative total of 70 confirmed cases had been reported from abroad and 6 cases had been cured.
自2月29日以来，由机场海关检疫转医疗机构筛查的人员累计2417人，日均127人，近一周来日均已达288人，3月18日高达479人。
Since 29 February, a total of 2,417 persons have been screened by the customs quarantine and medical institutions at the airport, with an average daily rate of 127, reaching an average of 288 a day in the past week and 479 on 18 March.
首都机场口岸日均入境人员约6000—8000人。
The average daily number of people entering the airport is 6,000 to 8,000.
飞友科技统计数据显示，仅3月18日就有24班入境航班。
There were 24 inbound flights on March 18 alone, according to Flying Friends technology statistics.
北京规定所有境外进京人员均应转送至集中观察点进行14天的隔离观察，与上海仅针对24个重点国家采取集中隔离措施相比，北京防控压力更大。
Beijing requires all foreign visitors to Beijing to be transferred to a centralized observation point for a 14-day quarantine, which is more stressful to control than the city's centralized quarantine measures, which target only 24 key countries.
北京市分配给沈阳入境人员的酒店有两家。
There are two hotels in Beijing that are allocated to Shenyang residents.
除了引导旅客填报个人健康信息，从接送到入住酒店，每一环节经手人都需签字。
In addition to guiding passengers to fill in personal health information, from pick-up to check-in hotel, every link of the handlers need to sign.
“谁负责接送，谁签字。
"Who will deliver and who will sign?
到宾馆，谁负责接待也要签字，而整套流程我们都需要全程跟随，忙不过来啊。
To the hotel, who is responsible for reception must also sign, and the whole process we need to follow, busy ah.
”一名负责对接沈阳旅客的工作人员向《财经》记者表示。
A staff member in charge of docking Shenyang passengers told Caijing.
“我是从大年三十一直干到现在，确定沈阳市无新增确诊病例后就到北京负责对接沈阳入境旅客。
"I have been working since the Chinese New Year's Eve until now, after confirming that there are no new confirmed cases in Shenyang, I went to Beijing to handle incoming passengers from Shenyang.
现在每天很多人入境，我们人手根本不够，这里的每一个人都是24小时连轴转，一天后再换另一拨人。
There are a lot of people coming in every day, we just don't have enough people. Everyone here has to go around 24 hours a day, and another group a day later.
”以上工作人员说。
"said the man.
根据中外航空公司报送的航班计划，3月16日-22日，中国内地和52个国家的102个境外航点保持定期航班飞行，当周计划执行2072班往返航班，其中客运1165班。
According to the flight plan submitted by Chinese and foreign airlines, 102 overseas destinations in China and 52 countries maintained regular flights from March 16 to 22, and a total of 2,072 round-trip flights, including 1165 passenger flights, are planned for the same week.
《财经》记者统计显示，这些航班中有202班飞往首都机场。
According to Caijing reporter statistics, 202 of these flights are to the Capital Airport.
随着疫情全球蔓延，中国民航局3月19日通告，以民航局3月12日官网发布的“国际航班信息发布（第5期）”为基准，每家航空公司在每条航线上的航班量只减不增。
With the global spread of the epidemic, China's Civil Aviation Administration on March 19, the Civil Aviation Administration issued the "International Flight Information Release (No. 5)," issued by the Civil Aviation Administration on March 12 as a benchmark for the number of flights per route.
